import React, { useEffect } from 'react' import { useLocation } from 'react-router-dom' function Certificate({result}) { const location = useLocation() const data = location.state useEffect(()=>{ console.warn(Object.keys(data.marks)) console.warn(Object.values(data.marks)) },[]) return ( <>

name: {data.name}

seat number: {data.seatno}

branch: {data.exam.branch}

sem: {data.exam.sem}

year: {data.exam.year}

Marks

  • sub1 : {data.marks.sub1}
  • sub2 : {data.marks.sub2}
  • sub3 : {data.marks.sub3}
  • sub4 : {data.marks.sub4}
  • sub5 : {data.marks.sub5}

SGPI: {data.sgpi}

remark: {data.remark}

) } export default Certificate
